Asụsụ Futop, Efutop (Ofutop), bụ asụsụ Ekoid nke Naijiria
E- na Efutop na-anọchite anya nganiihu klas maka "asụsụ", yiri Bantu ki- na KiSwahili.
Otu n'ime ọtụtụ asụsụ ndị yiri ya ma dị iche iche a na-asụ na mpaghara Cross River, mpaghara ya gụnyere obodo Abaragba yana Ekpokpa, Mkpura, Ndim, Okanga-Nkpansi, Okanga -Njimowan, na Okosura
Crabb na Ekoid Bantu Asusu make Ogoja sitere n'aka Maazị Anthony A
